<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Service Temporarily Unavailable</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
        Roboto, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #020617);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 90%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .status {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
      color: #f87171;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .actions a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 6px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      background: #2563eb;
      color: white;
      transition: background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .actions a:hover {
      background: #1d4ed8;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>

    <h1>Service Temporarily Unavailable</h1>

    <div class="status">Database offline</div>

    <p>
      Our database is currently unavailable or undergoing maintenance.
      No data has been lost. Please try again in a few moments.
    </p>

    <div class="actions">
      <a href="/">Go back home</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
      If this issue persists, the system is probably yelling at the cloud provider.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
